<i>noun</i>: 방화 [방ː화] <i>verb</i>: 방화하다 [방ː화하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>방화 [방ː화]</dt><br>
<dd>arson</dd><br>
<dd>일부러 불을 지름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of setting fire intentionally.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>방화하다 [방ː화하다]</dt><br>
<dd>arson</dd><br>
<dd>일부러 불을 지르다.</dd><br>
<dd>To set fire intentionally.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>